				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Guide for KITERS (BARD/DRUID/NECRO)
<br />
Do your standard kiting thing, let the mage summon a Water /pet no taunt for backstabs and have him cast velocity. Depending on the mob, mage starts nuking when the mob is at 50-70pct health. Mages rock to speed up kiting.
<br />

<br />
/Kaggers</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
